title: Five dead in new Azerbaijan-Armenia clash over disputed region
description: Five people have been killed in clashes between Azerbaijani troops and Armenian police in the contested region of Nagorno-Karabakh.

title: Israeli air force reservists skip training as protests against Netanyahu's reforms step up
description: Dozens of Israeli air force reservists will refuse to turn up to training drills in protest over controversial plans by Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu to overhaul the country's legal system.

title: Thousands left homeless by massive fire in Bangladeshi Rohingya refugee camp
description: A massive fire at an overcrowded Rohingya refugee camp in Bangladesh has left thousands homeless.

title: Fire and violence in Athens as protesters clash with riot police over rail disaster
description: Greek police were pelted with petrol bombs during clashes with protesters as anger continues to swell over a train crash which left 57 people dead.

title: The UN high seas treaty is a huge milestone - but there is a long way to go
description: The emotion as chairwoman Rena Lee announced that a UN high seas treaty had finally been agreed reflected her exhaustion, relief and the sheer human endeavour that multilateralism entails.

title: Two Ukrainian pilots undergo fighter jet assessment training in US
description: Two Ukrainian pilots are currently undergoing a training assessment in the US to fly American fighter jets, including F-16s.
